<h3 style="font-size: 30px; line-height: 32px;">Geocoding Desktop Tool</h3>
<h6 style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 40px;">The MAR Geocoder is a desktop application that employs web services to assign a location in the form of geographic coordinates.  It includes built in quality control tools to review records  and take advantage of several look-up tables for alternative names, abbreviations, misspellings, etc.  The resulting data adheres to the DCâ€™s addressing standard.</h6>
